---
title: Double-Roasted Cauliflower in Cheese Sauce with Walnut Gratin
description: This cauliflower casserole will be the crowning glory of your holiday table! The florets are first roasted for added depth and flavour, then smothered in a rich, cheesy sauce before topping them off with a walnut parmesan gratin that brings delectable, crunchy goodness to every bite!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/double-roasted-cauliflower-in-cheese-sauce-3c0e440d.jpg
